question: Ladu Kishore Swain, who passed away recently, was the current MP from which Lok Sabha constituency of Odisha?
explanation: Ladu Kishore Swain (71), the senior Biju Janata Dal (BJD) leader, has passed away in Bhubaneswar on 5 February 2019. He was elected to the 16th Lok Sabha in May 2014 from Aska constituency of Odisha.
